originalText.text:
Had a great experience. Upon arrival, the gentleman took my keys & provided me with the tag to pickup my vehicle at the end of my reservation. On the day I had to pickup my vehicle, I handed over the tag and had my car shortly thereafter. I would recommend.
Only downside was that I was charged an oversized fee for my 4 door jeep wrangler,  while the site said that oversized vehicles were those like Suburbans. But whatever, the garage felt safe to me & my car was returned in the same condition I left it in.
